Page 2, line 13, delete "applicable,".
Page 2, line 27, delete "(a)." and insert "(a)(1).".
Page 2, line 29, delete "a procedure" and insert "an examination".
Page 2, delete lines 32 through 33.
Page 2, line 34, delete "(e)" and insert "(d)".
Page 2, delete lines 39 through 42.
Delete page 3.
Renumber all SECTIONS consecutively.
and when so amended that said bill do pass.
